            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizzas are in the oven, combine the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash the<strong> rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once cooked, remove the pizzas from the oven and break the <strong>goats' cheese</strong> up all over them – these are your <strong>goats' cheese & red pepper pizzas</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
